settings.description: Mario uses the backdoor of Luigi's castle to destroy Luigi in one of the bowser suits (bowser suits are robots) also final bowser fight looking cool ngl
Bowser's secret airship, so Mario can head to Luigi's castle undetected.

How to make your level goal look good:
Height should be 26, otherwise ending background will be one tile higher. Goal Roulette should be 8 tiles from right edge of the level and 5 tiles up from ground
